%header
  %h1
    %a{:href => "/"} Ben Schwarz
    is a web architect hailing from Melbourne, Australia who has a strong focus on user experience and scalable content delivery. 
    
%section#content
  #recently
    %h2 Recently
    %ul
      - for article in @articles
        %li.post
          %p
            %a{:href => article_path(article)}= article.title
            %span.source
              from
              %a{:href => "/articles"} articles
      %li.post
        %p
          %a{:href => "#"} Why stopping ffolio development was one of the best things I could do for the project
          %span.source
            from
            %a{:href => "#"} articles
      %li
        %h3 Smoke
        %span.source
          from
          %a{:href => "#"} projects / github
        %p A Ruby based DSL to query and reinterpret the web
      %li
        %img{:src => "http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3438/3743345092_26704f3d3f_m.jpg"}
        %h3 How I roll
        %span.source
          from
          %a{:href => "#"} photos / flickr
        %p The contents of my crumpler, emptied on my desk then quickly neatened up when I realised there was a photo oppurtunity here
  #links
    %h2 Links
    %ul
      - for link in @links
        %li
          %a{:href => link.link}= link.description
  #projects
    %h2 Projects
    %ul
      - for project in @projects
        %li
          %a{:href => project[:url]}= project[:name]
  #presentations
    %h2 Presentations
    %ul
      - for presentation in @presentations
        %li
          %a{:href => presentation[:URL]}
            %img{:src => presentation[:ThumbnailSmallURL]}